-# Locals: teammate, position
- teammate = local_assigns.fetch(:teammate)
- position = local_assigns.fetch(:position)
- casual_name = teammate.person.casual_name.presence || teammate.person.display_name
- position_name = position.display_name

.alert.alert-light.border.mb-0
  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Goal of this page
  %p.mb-3
    See, criterion by criterion, what it would take for
    %strong= casual_name
    to be eligible for consideration of
    %strong= position_name
    — and where they already meet, are on track, or still need work.

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Context
  = render "shared/maap/definition"
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 Position / Title Change
  %p.mb-3
    This page is the detailed eligibility breakdown behind Grow by Position Change. Use it after choosing a current or target position to understand readiness with the same rules that drive the high-level Eligible / Not eligible yet signals.

  %h3.fw-semibold.mb-2 Specifics of this page
  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 How to read this page
  %ul.mb-3
    %li
      Each card is one eligibility criterion (business need, aspirational values, assignments, Ability Milestones, mileage, position ratings, and so on). Criteria that do not apply to this analysis are listed under Irrelevant criteria at the bottom.
    %li
      Cards start collapsed. Use
      %em Expand for details
      to see the month-by-month or requirement table; the footer still shows the criterion’s outcome when collapsed.
    %li
      Requirements may come from the position itself, department defaults, or organization defaults — the caption under the intro sentence tells you which.

  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 Example
  .border.rounded.p-3.bg-white.mb-3
    %p.mb-1.fw-semibold Criteria for Required Assignments…
    %p.small.text-muted.mb-2 Meeting on at least 80% of required assignments over the last 12 months.
    %p.small.mb-0
      %span.badge.text-bg-warning.me-1 Working to meet requirements
      Footer totals show Exceeding / Meeting / Miss counts so you can see what still needs attention.

  %h5.fw-semibold.mb-2 Status legend
  %ul.list-unstyled.mb-0
    %li.mb-1
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded-circle.me-2{class: "bg-success", style: "width:0.65rem;height:0.65rem;"}
      Eligible / Meeting eligibility — this criterion is met
    %li.mb-1
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded-circle.me-2{class: "bg-info", style: "width:0.65rem;height:0.65rem;"}
      On track to being eligible — not there yet, but trajectory looks good
    %li.mb-0
      %span.d-inline-block.rounded-circle.me-2{class: "bg-warning", style: "width:0.65rem;height:0.65rem;"}
      Working to meet requirements / No current business need — more progress or an open seat is still needed
